p.span: The closure continues through Thursday, May 7th. There will be a school board meeting on April 27th to make the final determination of our course of action. It appears that we will remain closed through this school year as a precaution to not overload our hospitals and healthcare workers. There are no definite answers on this matter and it could all change tomorrow. I am not trying to get anyone's hopes up or deflate anyone, but the reality is we have to continue to social distance, practice good hygiene and not have large gatherings which could have the potential to spread the virus. Please understand that we will follow Stillwater Public Health directives on what we can and cannot do. Read more...
